Input part with "\includegraphics" command:

Extracted figure filename: wd.jpg

Since there is only one "\includegraphics" command in the provided input, the output will be:

If there were more included graphic files, they would be listed one per line, separated by a newline character (\n). But in this case, there's only one file to print.
